Package: AccSamplingDesign
Title: Acceptance Sampling Plans Design
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Ha", "Truong", 
           email = "truongvietha87@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")), 
      person("Victor", "Miranda", role = c("ths", "rev")),  
      person("Roger", "Kissling", role = c("ths", "rev"))  
    )
Description: An R package for designing and analyzing acceptance sampling plans.
    Supports both attribute-based (binomial) and variable-based (normal and beta)
    sampling. Includes tools for measurement error adjustments and OC curve
    visualization, enabling quality control for fractional and compositional data.
